headline: Procter & Gamble (PG) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: P&G (PG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +4.74% and +1.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
